\n另外，以美國為首嘅西方，最終目標唔單止係做生意，而係生意要按佢哋定落嘅遊戲規則之下做，而且呢個生意對手亦須要接納西方嘅價值體系，咁佢哋做生意先做得安心。中共符唔符合呢啲條件？侵侵上台後，對華政策大幅改變，正好話我哋知，佢哋唔再相信中共現在以至將來會符合條件。最徹底嘅解決方法，當然就係消滅中共啦，而呢度香港就可以發揮作用了。"},{"pid":"9f187c03efd417e1a64ed6bb6419e698d7e0fade","tid":1505610,"uid":130346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:54:02.000Z","msg":"學術PO強推"},{"pid":"db115ad2f891c3b3577e5a4d103e2db7f5a0043b","tid":1505610,"uid":54125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:58:52.000Z","msg":"分析得好好<br />\n放任政府搞唔死香港係終需一死<br />\n而家我哋係救緊香港"},{"pid":"48831e30a4076a08f67740228fd23568949631e1","tid":1505610,"uid":107297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T18:05:48.000Z","msg":"希望西方真係會同中共打意識形態戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n否則唔單止香港，西方都會比中國慢慢滲透統戰染紅"},{"pid":"7bab15dfe45d6213e25379d7f6032cb2608e34b0","tid":1505610,"uid":261354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f001941c9b8a39bf3e458d7d415fc05d0eff0288","tid":1505610,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4370679147e944476f107a47cf686766f75f531d","tid":1505610,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"017e3a955c72ec583c06408b7c6cf2dd1cf4d60e","tid":1505610,"uid":73234,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T15:39:09.000Z","msg":"美國可以單方面唔俾港元掛鈎美金咩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:15:29.000Z","msg":"當然可以"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:23:43.000Z","msg":"how<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T18:31:04.000Z","msg":"禁止使用美國Swift 系統進行貨幣匯款 禁止在港銀行美元結算<br />\n<br />\n無得用美元即刻跪低"},{"pid":"5dcf7f5dcf40477282b7f395ee9a7ac82ac863f3","tid":1505610,"uid":61082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a81b98173636bf336b21ebb4e8fd1604334624c","tid":1505610,"uid":35104,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f886f54c80e969a8e43945be9c274f18965ed2a8","tid":1505610,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike"